author: Jeremy Jahns
description:
Sam Wilson makes his big screen debut as Captain America! Does the movie bring us into a new era of the MCU? Is it fun as an action movie romp? Or does it feel like the reported re-shoots are true? Here's my review of CAPTAIN AMERICA: BRAVE NEW WORLD!

#CaptainAmerica #CaptainAmericaBraveNewWorld
title: Captain America: Brave New World - Movie Review
